<beast version="1.10">

    <!--
        Synthetic OU time-series benchmark matching StanVsBeastOUBenchmarkTest.

        Both cases use a fully irregular grid: T=300 observations gives 299 distinct
        adjacent intervals. perturbEachIteration="true" alternates a tiny change to
        the first rho parameter before every timed evaluation, matching the MCMC
        scenario where A changes and transition caches must be rebuilt.

        Edit warmup and timedIterations here without rebuilding BEAST.
    -->

